steps.name: Given Check if Admin is logged in or not for the Class Module
Then Admin should be on Manage Class Page in Class module
Given Admin is on the Edit Class Popup window in Class module
When Admin Update the fields with valid data and click save on the Class PopUp from "Class" with scenario name "editClassWithOnlyMandatoryFields"
Then Admin gets message "class details updated Successfully " and see the updated values in data table on the Class table from "Class" with scenario name "editClassWithOnlyMandatoryFields"
